如果我認為我們通過達達·諾爾的植入物
And if I think we're putting Dada Noe's life in danger

345
00:24:00,848 --> 00:24:02,557
讓他生命垂危
by tinkering with that implant,

346
00:24:02,557 --> 00:24:04,977
我會通過星際艦隊
I will unleash the full weight of Starfleet

347
00:24:04,977 --> 00:24:06,353
對此次任務施壓
on this whole operation.

348
00:24:06,353 --> 00:24:09,277
嘿 我們討論的可是一個要出售超級武器的傢伙
Oy, we're talking about a bloke who's selling superweapons

349
00:24:09,277 --> 00:24:10,957
他會把東西賣給任何有拉蒂金卡的三流恐怖分子
to any third-rate terrorist with a Latinum card.

350
00:24:10,957 --> 00:24:12,737
聽仔細了 滿腦子廢品的傢伙
Listen carefully, Junkyard.

351
00:24:12,737 --> 00:24:15,757
星際艦隊不執行暗殺任務
Starfleet does not do assassinations.

352
00:24:15,757 --> 00:24:18,337
唉 別再滿腦子的惦記著你的最高指導原則了
Ay, don't get your prime directives in a bunch.

353
00:24:18,337 --> 00:24:20,497
不會讓你親自下場弄髒手的
You are not going to get your hands dirty

354
00:24:20,497 --> 00:24:22,797
也不會壞了你升艦長的前程
and mess up your chances of becoming captain.

355
00:24:22,797 --> 00:24:24,171
我可是頂尖科學官
I'm a top-tier science officer.

356
00:24:24,171 --> 00:24:25,200
屁股擰成麻花了
Butt pretzel.

357
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,517
就是個死板精
Tight-ass.

358
00:24:26,517 --> 00:24:27,957
真是太不尊重人了
So disrespectful.

359
00:24:27,957 --> 00:24:30,144
只要加勒特和法茲切斷了組件的鏈接
Soon as Garrett and Fuzz sever that link...

360
00:24:32,617 --> 00:24:34,457
他就隨便我們拿捏了
...he'll be under our control, 

361
00:24:34,457 --> 00:24:36,317
我會和澤弗一起制服他
and I'll take him down with the help of Zeph.

362
00:24:43,957 --> 00:24:45,077
一下搞定
That's what I call a hit.

363
00:24:45,077 --> 00:24:45,597
只需一下
One.

364
00:24:45,597 --> 00:24:47,493
達達·諾爾會被拘留 他的病原體會被沒收
Dada Noe and his pathogen will be in custody

365
00:24:47,494 --> 00:24:50,331
這一切會在賣家出現在巴拉姆空間站之前就完成
before the buyers can even show up to the Baraam.

366
00:24:50,737 --> 00:24:52,377
速戰速決
And we are in and out.

367
00:24:52,377 --> 00:24:53,637
呃
Mm.

368
00:24:53,637 --> 00:24:55,177
算了
Meh.

369
00:24:56,570 --> 00:24:57,571
啥
Meh?

370
00:24:58,017 --> 00:24:59,817
我有個更簡單的辦法
I have a simpler idea.

371
00:24:59,817 --> 00:25:02,877
表情很絕望 我看的出來
♪ Desperate, I can tell ♪

372
00:25:02,877 --> 00:25:05,079
所有的祈求
♪ All that begging ♪

373
00:25:05,079 --> 00:25:07,114
都像是為你量身訂做的
♪ Suits you well. ♪

374
00:25:08,117 --> 00:25:09,983
現在打爆我的手機
♪ Blowing up my phone now ♪

375
00:25:09,984 --> 00:25:12,086
我向上 你低頭
♪ Going up, you bow down ♪

376
00:25:12,086 --> 00:25:14,654
看看是誰需要誰
♪ Look at who needs who... ♪

377
00:25:14,655 --> 00:25:17,391
歡迎歡迎 達達·諾爾先生
Welcome, Monsieur Dada Noe.

378
00:25:17,391 --> 00:25:20,697
您的到來使巴拉姆空間站蓬蓽生輝
We're honored to have you here at the Baraam.

379
00:25:20,697 --> 00:25:23,217
我是維羅妮卡·杜·弗朗克 這裡的店主
I am Veronique du Franc, the proprietor.

380
00:25:23,217 --> 00:25:25,197
我早就預約我的套間了吧
I told them to have my suite ready.

381
00:25:25,197 --> 00:25:26,437
當然 先生
Mais oui, monsieur.

382
00:25:26,437 --> 00:25:28,501
請允許我帶您到房間裡
May I escort you to your quarters?

383
00:25:28,877 --> 00:25:29,937
請隨我來
Come.

384
00:25:31,057 --> 00:25:33,274
我們有最好的…
We have the most exquisite...

385
00:25:33,274 --> 00:25:35,297
我簡直不敢相信你會信任這個反社會的瘋子
I can't believe you're trusting this sociopath.

386
00:25:35,297 --> 00:25:36,157
上尉
Well, Lieutenant,

387
00:25:36,157 --> 00:25:37,677
你做好自己的事
you got to do what you got to do,

388
00:25:37,678 --> 00:25:39,057
我知道怎麼跟反社會瘋子打交道
and I'm kind of familiar with sociopaths.

389
00:25:39,597 --> 00:25:41,115
我說了別帶我來
I said don't bring me.

390
00:25:43,437 --> 00:25:45,752
我想您的旅程一切順利 先生
I trust your trip was without incident, monsieur.

391
00:25:45,752 --> 00:25:49,137
你的團隊倒是幫我把一切都打點好了
Well, your people made everything easy.

392
00:25:49,137 --> 00:25:50,437
不勝榮幸
Our pleasure.

393
00:25:50,437 --> 00:25:51,597
我們到了
Here we are.

394
00:25:58,417 --> 00:26:00,557
太俗氣了
So tacky.

395
00:26:01,157 --> 00:26:03,004
但我想這就是你出名的地方
But I guess that's what you're known for.

396
00:26:08,568 --> 00:26:09,602
這是什麼？
What's this?

397
00:26:09,602 --> 00:26:11,003
這東西叫相位轉移器
It's called a phase pod.

398
00:26:11,302 --> 00:26:13,380
我的某位客戶送給我的禮物
A client of mine gave it to me as a gift,

399
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:15,715
我自己也有一個
and I got one for myself, too.

400
00:26:26,011 --> 00:26:26,927
你在做什麼
What are you doing?

401
00:26:26,927 --> 00:26:28,629
宇宙中的一切
Everything in the universe vibrates

402
00:26:28,629 --> 00:26:30,230
都以特定的波長振動
on a certain wavelength.

403
00:26:30,777 --> 00:26:32,178
該死
Damn it.

404
00:26:33,834 --> 00:26:35,236
把箱子還給我
Give me back my case.

405
00:26:35,236 --> 00:26:36,637
我拒絕
No.

406
00:26:38,427 --> 00:26:41,102
維修費從你的押金裡出
That's coming out of your security deposit.

407
00:26:41,577 --> 00:26:43,744
相位轉移器則會改變
The phase pod changes the wavelength

408
00:26:43,744 --> 00:26:45,346
接觸到的任何東西的物質波長
of whatever they touch.

409
00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:48,860
我和你不在同一相位 你也不和我在同一相位
I am out of phase with you, and you're out of phase with me.

410
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:52,786
但是我 跟你的箱子在同一相位
I am, however, in phase with your case.

411
00:26:55,352 --> 00:26:57,577
然後我會把它拿走
And I will be taking it with me.

412
00:26:58,652 --> 00:27:01,395
你根本不知道你挑起了什麼
You have no idea what you've started.

413
00:27:03,597 --> 00:27:05,266
哎呀
Whoopsie.

414
00:27:11,102 --> 00:27:12,138
不錯嘛
Impressive.

415
00:27:12,677 --> 00:27:13,727
你真的是普通人類嗎
Are you sure you're human?

416
00:27:15,177 --> 00:27:15,977
多數時候是
Most days.

417
00:27:15,977 --> 00:27:17,511
謝謝你
Thank you.

418
00:27:50,411 --> 00:27:53,247
把箱子給我
Give me the case.

419
00:28:25,146 --> 00:28:26,613
你是誰
Who are you?

420
00:28:36,757 --> 00:28:39,559
他從那兒走了 那兒那兒 走那邊
He went that way. That way, that way, that way!

421
00:28:51,102 --> 00:28:52,239
哇 外星人
Oh, aliens.

422
00:28:52,239 --> 00:28:53,227
還是裸體的
Naked aliens.

423
00:28:53,227 --> 00:28:54,215
澤弗 快追
Go, Zeph, go.

424
00:29:13,327 --> 00:29:16,063
他往休息室去了 天哪 他們走得真快
He's headed to the lounge. Man, they're moving fast.

425
00:29:16,063 --> 00:29:17,730
梅爾 他朝你來了
Melle, he's coming to you.

426
00:29:20,667 --> 00:29:21,468
哎呀
Yikes.

427
00:29:31,643 --> 00:29:33,340
沒事沒事 我還好
No, it's okay. I'm all right.

428
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:34,177
梅爾 有看到目標嗎
Melle, you got him?

429
00:29:34,177 --> 00:29:34,852
看到了
Got him.

430
00:29:38,452 --> 00:29:39,427
哎呀
Ooh-la-la!

431
00:29:39,427 --> 00:29:40,887
嗨 親愛的
Ay, amor.

432
00:31:51,117 --> 00:31:52,877
不可能
That's not possible.

433
00:31:52,877 --> 00:31:54,154
它已經被我銷毀了
I had that destroyed.

434
00:31:54,727 --> 00:31:56,422
不
No. No!

435
00:31:59,577 --> 00:32:00,527
這不可能
It's not possible.

436
00:32:00,527 --> 00:32:01,677
你知道那件武器
You knew that weapon.

437
00:32:01,677 --> 00:32:02,852
是什麼
What is it?

438
00:32:05,552 --> 00:32:06,777
回答我
What is it?

439
00:32:09,102 --> 00:32:11,872
行 那就來硬的
Fine. The hard way.

440
00:32:44,852 --> 00:32:47,477
永恆的祈求者懇請覲見
The Eternal Supplicant begs approach.

441
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:36,760
（人族帝國）

442
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:41,160
（人族帝國）
（上輩子）

443
00:32:44,852 --> 00:32:47,477
永恆的祈求者懇請覲見
The Eternal Supplicant begs approach.

444
00:32:47,477 --> 00:32:49,042
准了
You have my permission.

445
00:32:56,552 --> 00:32:59,177
參見至高無上的女皇陛下
All hail Her Most Imperial Majesty,

446
00:32:59,177 --> 00:33:00,287
崇上國母
Mother of the Fatherland,

447
00:33:00,287 --> 00:33:01,852
-瓦肯領主  -你帶來的是什麼
- Overlord of Vulc... - What is it?

448
00:33:03,457 --> 00:33:05,359
它完成了 陛下
It is finished, Your Majesty.

449
00:33:08,677 --> 00:33:10,311
我的工程師們在哪
Where are my engineers?

450
00:33:11,727 --> 00:33:15,969
他們 他們在完工後結束了自己的生命
They... they took their own lives upon completion.

451
00:33:20,907 --> 00:33:23,577
你在為誰流淚 桑
Who is the tear for, San?

452
00:33:25,779 --> 00:33:27,648
說
Speak.

453
00:33:28,127 --> 00:33:30,751
是為您 陛下
It is for you, Majesty.

454
00:33:31,618 --> 00:33:33,787
這都是
It is all...

455
00:33:35,922 --> 00:33:37,591
為了您
...for you.

456
00:33:46,533 --> 00:33:49,269
我再問你 桑
I asked you a question, San.

457
00:33:51,037 --> 00:33:52,739
你為何為我而哭
Why do you cry for me?

458
00:33:57,427 --> 00:33:58,452
看著我
Look at me.

459
00:34:02,327 --> 00:34:05,752
你還記得我們是誰嗎
Do you remember who we were?

460
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:09,022
在這一切之前
Before all this.

461
00:34:09,022 --> 00:34:11,857
好奇的男孩
The curious boy.

462
00:34:11,858 --> 00:34:14,628
天真的女孩
The innocent girl.

463
00:34:15,852 --> 00:34:18,077
我只記得我的失敗 陛下
I only remember my failure, Majesty.

464
00:34:18,077 --> 00:34:20,934
別對我撒謊
Don't lie to me.

465
00:34:23,302 --> 00:34:29,208
為了活下去 我們付出了別人無法想像的代價
We were the only ones who could understand the cost to stay alive.

466
00:34:29,209 --> 00:34:32,045
我們是一個集體
We made a team.

467
00:34:32,045 --> 00:34:35,777
彼此依靠 不可分割
We needed each other, didn't we?

468
00:34:35,777 --> 00:34:41,587
記得那時我們是靠著什麼話語 彼此支撐著活下來的嗎
What did we say to carry each other through, to survive together?

469
00:34:41,588 --> 00:34:43,424
我們雖為兩人
We are two...

470
00:34:45,191 --> 00:34:46,927
但為一體
But one.

471
00:34:46,927 --> 00:34:49,463
我們雖為兩人 但為一體
We are two but one.

472
00:34:50,327 --> 00:34:51,732
如果我說
If I said then,

473
00:34:51,732 --> 00:34:53,233
「我們逃跑吧」
"Let's run away,

474
00:34:53,233 --> 00:34:55,227
「逃離這場競爭」
"let's flee this competition

475
00:34:55,227 --> 00:34:57,937
「以及把我們和人族聯繫在一起的一切」
and everything that binds us to Terra,"

476
00:34:57,938 --> 00:35:00,306
你會說什麼呢
what would you have said?

477
00:35:03,477 --> 00:35:07,681
您問這個問題的時機 比您認為的更富意味
The timing of your question is more poetic than you know.

478
00:35:10,277 --> 00:35:12,646
我會答應您
I would have said yes.

479
00:35:19,993 --> 00:35:21,327
只會在當時
Then.

480
00:35:23,827 --> 00:35:25,127
那麼現在呢
But now?

481
00:35:26,827 --> 00:35:31,827
您本可以在您的治下創造一些美好的東西
You could have made something beautiful with your reign.

482
00:35:31,827 --> 00:35:34,652
然而 您卻選擇了讓人製造此物
Instead, you chose to build this.

483
00:35:34,652 --> 00:35:37,502
這意味著我熟知的那個天真女孩
That means that innocent girl I knew,

484
00:35:37,502 --> 00:35:39,846
她已經
she has been...

485
00:35:41,452 --> 00:35:42,727
死了
...murdered.

486
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:44,885
怎麼回事
What is this?

487
00:35:46,352 --> 00:35:47,820
你
You...

488
00:35:47,821 --> 00:35:50,657
你服用了一樣的毒藥?
You took the same poison?

489
00:35:52,292 --> 00:35:55,077
不 我不許你死
No! I forbid you to die!

490
00:35:55,077 --> 00:35:58,552
沒有人願意活在
No one wants to live

491
00:35:58,552 --> 00:36:01,502
您的統治中 皇帝
in your world, Emperor.

492
00:36:01,502 --> 00:36:04,571
你就是個怪物
You are a monster!

493
00:36:32,152 --> 00:36:35,677
這是什麼令人愉快的地方
And what delightful place is this?

494
00:36:35,677 --> 00:36:36,802
一個安全屋
A safe house.

495
00:36:36,802 --> 00:36:39,505
但對你而言也許不是
But maybe not so safe for you.

496
00:36:39,506 --> 00:36:41,452
既然你是31區的
You are Section 31.

497
00:36:41,452 --> 00:36:44,427
你為什麼不拷問我以獲取答案
Why aren't you torturing answers out of me?

498
00:36:44,427 --> 00:36:46,127
你是個暴君
You're a tyrant.

499
00:36:46,127 --> 00:36:47,527
貨真價實的
A real one.

500
00:36:47,527 --> 00:36:49,227
折磨起不到半點作用
Torture wouldn't work.

501
00:36:49,227 --> 00:36:52,217
你怎麼會這麼了解我這種人呢
How do you know so much about people like me?

502
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:57,924
是在哪裡學來的暴君手段 而且學得很到位
You learned tyranny somewhere, and you learned hard.

503
00:36:59,177 --> 00:37:01,294
藏著掖著 只證明了你的軟弱
If you have to hide it, that's a weakness.

504
00:37:03,764 --> 00:37:06,365
而我 不能容許搭檔有這種弱點
And I can't have that in a partner.

505
00:37:06,366 --> 00:37:07,702
我們可算不上搭檔
We're not partners.

506
00:37:07,702 --> 00:37:08,852
不是嗎
No?

507
00:37:08,852 --> 00:37:10,852
我可是幫了大忙了
I've been very helpful.

508
00:37:10,852 --> 00:37:12,777
你的計劃行不通
You had a plan that couldn't work.

509
00:37:12,777 --> 00:37:13,852
而我給了你更好的
I gave you a better one.

510
00:37:13,852 --> 00:37:16,302
你讓我嚐到了那種刺激
You gave me a taste of the action,

511
00:37:16,302 --> 00:37:17,978
還明知道我會上癮
knowing I'd want more.

512
00:37:19,613 --> 00:37:21,247
你需要我
You need me.

513
00:37:21,247 --> 00:37:23,483
你選擇了我
You chose me.

514
00:37:25,551 --> 00:37:26,653
為什麼呢
Why?

515
00:37:26,653 --> 00:37:29,077
不管你認為你的任務是什麼
Whatever you believed your mission was,

516
00:37:29,077 --> 00:37:31,252
這遠比你想像的更糟糕
it's worse than you thought.

517
00:37:31,252 --> 00:37:35,677
事關數億萬生命 時間緊迫
Billions of lives are at stake, and time is short.

518
00:37:35,677 --> 00:37:39,465
你先讓我了解你 我才能告訴你
Tell me you, and I will tell you me.

519
00:37:39,465 --> 00:37:43,527
要想合作 我得知根知底
The only way this works is if I know exactly

520
00:37:43,527 --> 00:37:45,627
說出你的身份
who I'm dealing with.

521
00:37:57,217 --> 00:37:59,527
我也不屬於這個時代
I'm not from this time, either.

522
00:38:01,202 --> 00:38:03,527
我出生於20世紀的地球
I was born on Earth, 20th century.

523
00:38:03,527 --> 00:38:07,027
這麼說你已經350歲高齡了
You are 350 years old?

524
00:38:07,027 --> 00:38:08,428
差不多
More or less.

525
00:38:08,428 --> 00:38:10,864
大部分時間我在冬眠艙裡
I slept most of that time.

526
00:38:12,427 --> 00:38:13,834
在我被流放之後
After my exile.

527
00:38:16,637 --> 00:38:18,839
優生戰爭
The Eugenics Wars.

528
00:38:21,411 --> 00:38:25,145
強化人
Augments...

529
00:38:25,145 --> 00:38:26,747
奪走了我的星球
took my planet.

530
00:38:28,048 --> 00:38:30,050
我的家鄉
My home.

531
00:38:35,421 --> 00:38:38,524
當時我們差不多有十個人在戰鬥
There was maybe ten of us who fought.

532
00:38:38,524 --> 00:38:41,995
我認識的人不是挨了一槍就是挨了一刀
Everyone I knew either took a bullet or a blade.

533
00:38:42,827 --> 00:38:44,962
我也還以顏色
But I gave some back.

534
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,734
這讓她注意到了我
She noticed me.

535
00:38:49,077 --> 00:38:52,271
那個屠殺我家人的強化人
The Augment who slaughtered my family.

536
00:38:52,271 --> 00:38:57,343
他們叫她 被標記的吉裡
They called her Giri the Marked.

537
00:38:57,343 --> 00:38:59,178
她收留了我
She took me in.

538
00:38:59,179 --> 00:39:02,577
讓我比任何人類都強大
Made me stronger than any human should be.

539
00:39:02,577 --> 00:39:04,452
她把我撕成碎片
She ripped me apart

540
00:39:04,452 --> 00:39:07,519
然後把我重塑成了她軍隊裡的又一個強化人
and turned me into another Augment for her army.

541
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:10,877
我做了很多可怕的事
And I did terrible things.

542
00:39:10,877 --> 00:39:15,028
卻是為你這樣的怪物效力
All for a monster like you.

543
00:39:16,797 --> 00:39:20,827
因為對於暴君來說 永遠只有一個選擇
Because for tyrants, there is only one choice:

544
00:39:22,277 --> 00:39:23,837
殺戮
murder.

545
00:39:25,138 --> 00:39:26,900
但你卻沒殺掉我
You haven't killed me.

546
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:29,910
暫時而已
Yet.

547
00:39:35,827 --> 00:39:37,877
我之所以能認出那個武器
I recognized the weapon because

548
00:39:37,877 --> 00:39:40,902
因為它是我下令造的
I ordered it to be built.

549
00:39:43,452 --> 00:39:45,127
召集你的人手
Gather your people.

550
00:39:45,127 --> 00:39:47,427
每個人都得派上用場
We're gonna need every one of them.

551
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:02,920
（加密傳訊2）

552
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:07,380
（加密傳訊2）
（天賜之物）

553
00:40:24,377 --> 00:40:25,977
在我的宇宙裡
In my universe,

554
00:40:25,977 --> 00:40:27,577
陰謀重重 政敵環伺
there were always plotters.

555
00:40:27,577 --> 00:40:29,040
政變層出不窮
Always a coup.

556
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:32,352
所以我造了一件武器來終結所有威脅
So I built a weapon to end all threats.

557
00:40:33,252 --> 00:40:35,277
我稱之為
I called it

558
00:40:35,277 --> 00:40:36,627
「天賜之物」
the Godsend.

559
00:40:37,652 --> 00:40:39,577
它會引發一種連鎖反應
It triggers a chain reaction,

560
00:40:39,577 --> 00:40:42,102
就像病毒一樣在群星間傳播
like a virus passing between planets.

561
00:40:42,102 --> 00:40:44,583
所到之處 一切都將化為灰燼
Everything in its path incinerates.

562
00:40:44,584 --> 00:40:47,527
整個象限都會消失
An entire quadrant would be lost.

563
00:40:47,527 --> 00:40:49,977
如果我的敵人成功殺死了我
If my enemies managed to kill me,

564
00:40:49,977 --> 00:40:52,725
那也不會有東西留給他統治
there would be nothing left to rule.

565
00:40:55,527 --> 00:40:57,302
有個小問題
Yeah, hi. Quick question.

566
00:40:57,302 --> 00:40:57,864
不好意思
Sorry.

567
00:40:57,864 --> 00:41:00,102
就一個很小很小的問題
Yeah, no. Uh, just a qu-- it's just a quick one.

568
00:41:00,102 --> 00:41:03,536
這是天賜之物還是天賜之暮
Is it Godsend or God's End?

569
00:41:04,702 --> 00:41:05,877
天賜之物還是天賜之暮
Godsend or God's End?

570
00:41:05,877 --> 00:41:07,327
我不明白你說的有什麼區別
I don't hear a difference in what you're saying.

571
00:41:07,327 --> 00:41:10,752
聽不出來嗎 「物」和「暮」
Really? Really? Godsend. God's End.

572
00:41:10,752 --> 00:41:11,652
我還是沒聽明白
Yeah, I'm still not getting it.

573
00:41:11,652 --> 00:41:12,652
天賜之物是...
The Godsend is...

574
00:41:12,652 --> 00:41:14,477
噢 天賜之物 我現在聽清楚了
Wait, Godsend. I hear it now.

575
00:41:14,477 --> 00:41:16,252
-天賜之物 不是暮  -物
- It's Godsend. No apostrophe. - Send.

576
00:41:16,252 --> 00:41:17,818
天賜之物就在這個宇宙
The Godsend is here.

577
00:41:17,818 --> 00:41:20,377
怎麼會 那可是另一個宇宙的物品
How? It's from another universe.

578
00:41:20,377 --> 00:41:22,127
我不知道 但那個人剛剛就拿著它
I don't know, but that man had it.

579
00:41:22,127 --> 00:41:23,877
你以為是達達·諾伊的那個人
The one that you think is Dada Noe.

580
00:41:24,402 --> 00:41:25,902
我們都知道是達達·諾伊的那個人
The one we know is Dada Noe.

581
00:41:25,902 --> 00:41:29,077
不 他不可能是你們的達達·諾伊 
No, he's not your Dada Noe. He can't be.

582
00:41:29,077 --> 00:41:30,502
他來自人族帝國
He's from the Terran Empire,

583
00:41:30,502 --> 00:41:32,002
是他把天賜之物帶來這裡
and he brought the Godsend here.

584
00:41:32,002 --> 00:41:34,852
不然他根本不可能知道那到底是什麼
That's the only way he can know about it.

585
00:41:34,852 --> 00:41:36,702
既然我們已經抓到他了
And since we have him locked up tight,

586
00:41:36,702 --> 00:41:38,077
我要親自審訊他
I'll interrogate him.

587
00:41:38,077 --> 00:41:40,152
絕對不行 不能信這個女人說的話
No, no, no. We cannot trust a single word this woman says.

588
00:41:40,152 --> 00:41:40,877
是啊
Yeah.

589
00:41:40,877 --> 00:41:42,327
她害死了梅爾
She cost us Melle.

590
00:41:42,327 --> 00:41:44,377
只有她知道我們面對的是什麼人
She's the only one who knows what we're dealing with.

591
00:41:44,377 --> 00:41:46,252
也就是她自己說的 小兄弟
Yeah, well, so she says, little bro.

592
00:41:46,252 --> 00:41:46,927
小?
Little?

593
00:41:47,827 --> 00:41:49,452
這是身材羞辱
Scale-shamer!

594
00:41:49,452 --> 00:41:51,252
微生物比恐龍更長壽
Microbes outlasted dinosaurs!

595
00:41:51,252 --> 00:41:52,977
冷靜點 我要說的是
Calm your boots. What I'm saying is...

596
00:41:52,977 --> 00:41:55,988
我要尿在你的裝甲上 直到你全身生鏽
I will piss in your suit until you go all rusty like!

597
00:41:55,989 --> 00:41:57,677
這一切都是她搞砸的
...that she's the reason this is all bollixed up.

598
00:41:57,677 --> 00:41:59,002
她導致了梅爾的死
She's the reason Melle's dead, 

599
00:41:59,002 --> 00:42:01,152
她也是我們被派來這的原因
and she's the reason we're in the ass end of the galaxy.

600
00:42:01,152 --> 00:42:02,295
聽好了
Listen up.

601
00:42:05,327 --> 00:42:07,452
喬久和我回船上去
Georgiou and I are gonna go back to the ship.

602
00:42:07,452 --> 00:42:09,877
達達·諾伊是我們與天賜之物的唯一聯繫
Dada Noe is our only link to the Godsend,

603
00:42:10,503 --> 00:42:13,606
所以我們要找他談談
so we're gonna have a little chat with him.

604
00:42:26,119 --> 00:42:27,420
幹什麼
What?

605
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:29,354
她叫菲莉帕·喬久
Her name is Philippa Georgiou,

606
00:42:29,355 --> 00:42:31,402
至高無上的女皇陛下
Her Most Imperial Majesty.

607
00:42:31,402 --> 00:42:33,025
崇上國母
Mother of the Fatherland.

608
00:42:33,026 --> 00:42:34,527
瓦肯領主
Overlord of Vulcan.

609
00:42:34,527 --> 00:42:37,027
克羅諾斯征服者 安多利女王
Dominus of Qo'noS, Regina Andor,

610
00:42:37,027 --> 00:42:40,365
菲莉帕·喬久·奧古斯都·伊波尼亞斯·塞塔瑞斯
Philippa Georgiou Augustus Iaponius Centarius.

611
00:42:40,826 --> 00:42:41,927
酷
Cool.

612
00:42:41,927 --> 00:42:42,977
配薯條的嗎
That come with fries?

613
00:42:44,427 --> 00:42:45,429
很好笑 對吧
That was good, right?

614
00:42:48,077 --> 00:42:48,902
好吧
Okay.

615
00:42:48,902 --> 00:42:51,410
每次你不直接回答她的問題
Every time you don't answer her questions directly,

616
00:42:51,411 --> 00:42:54,547
女皇陛下就會狠狠地打你的臉
Her Majesty will punch you in your face.

617
00:42:54,547 --> 00:42:55,502
好吧
Fine.

618
00:42:57,327 --> 00:42:58,777
我是達達
I'm Dada.

619
00:42:58,777 --> 00:43:01,077
達達·諾伊 先念達達 再是諾伊
Dada Noe. Just Dada, then Noe.

620
00:43:01,077 --> 00:43:02,227
就是這樣 沒有中間
That's it. No in-betweens.

621
00:43:02,552 --> 00:43:04,389
然後 我
And I, uh...

622
00:43:04,390 --> 00:43:08,794
我以前在瓦特殖民地開過一家病理學實驗室
I used to run a pathology lab in the Watt Colonies.

623
00:43:14,567 --> 00:43:16,068
搞什麼鬼
What the shit, man?!

624
00:43:16,069 --> 00:43:19,305
你明明說揍我臉的會是她
You said that she was gonna be doing the face punching!

625
00:43:19,305 --> 00:43:22,708
現在我倆都說謊了 你不是那個達達
So now we both have lied. You are not that Dada.

626
00:43:23,877 --> 00:43:26,145
你是那些人口中說的他的鏡像版本
You're what these people call his Mirror.

627
00:43:27,952 --> 00:43:30,627
你來自人族帝國
You came here from the Terran Empire,

628
00:43:30,627 --> 00:43:32,977
而且還帶來了天賜之物
and you brought the Godsend.

629
00:43:32,977 --> 00:43:34,487
什麼天賜之物
What's the Godsend?

630
00:43:35,888 --> 00:43:38,527
我自己的軍事委員會曾想要廢黜我
My own war council tried to depose me.

631
00:43:38,527 --> 00:43:41,527
你知道我是怎麼說服元帥開口的嗎
Do you know how I convinced the field marshal to talk?

632
00:43:50,470 --> 00:43:51,704
我曾是個管理員
I was an administrator

633
00:43:51,704 --> 00:43:53,727
在帝國裡的武器設施工作
at an Imperial weapons facility on Terra.

634
00:43:54,627 --> 00:43:55,277
沒錯
Uh, yeah.

635
00:43:55,277 --> 00:43:58,511
天賜之物被存放在我管理的設施中
The Godsend was stored at my facility.

636
00:43:59,877 --> 00:44:01,977
大多數人認為這只是一個傳說
Most thought it was a legend,

637
00:44:01,977 --> 00:44:03,827
但我知道這是真的
but I knew it was real.

638
00:44:03,827 --> 00:44:05,302
所以你想賣掉它
So you tried to sell it.

639
00:44:05,302 --> 00:44:06,451
是 是的
Yeah, yeah.

640
00:44:06,452 --> 00:44:10,190
我想靠得來的收益安靜地生活在這裡
I wanted to live here quietly on its proceeds.

641
00:44:10,190 --> 00:44:11,857
你是怎麼來到我們的宇宙的
How did you get to our universe?

642
00:44:16,162 --> 00:44:17,930
當時發生了一場離子風暴
There was an ion storm.

643
00:44:17,930 --> 00:44:19,552
實際上是兩場
Two of them, actually.

644
00:44:19,552 --> 00:44:22,827
它們像對好了表一樣準時相遇
And when they converged, which they do like clockwork,

645
00:44:22,827 --> 00:44:26,027
撕裂了帝國邊界某處的時空
they ripped something open on the fringes of the Empire--

646
00:44:26,027 --> 00:44:27,827
他們稱之為異象
an anomaly, they called it--

647
00:44:27,827 --> 00:44:30,652
但這實際上是一條通道
but it was a passageway

648
00:44:30,652 --> 00:44:33,413
從人族帝國通往這裡
to get to this place from the Terran Empire.

649
00:44:34,902 --> 00:44:38,827
從你們宇宙的新月星雲穿出
Comes out through your Crescent Nebula.

650
00:44:38,827 --> 00:44:41,177
至少目前還是鮮有人知的
Few know about it. For now.

651
00:44:41,177 --> 00:44:43,756
但它四小時後會重新開放
But it'll open again in four hours.

652
00:44:43,756 --> 00:44:46,302
那本來是我要去見買家的時間
That's when I was supposed to be meeting my buyer.

653
00:44:46,727 --> 00:44:48,777
你知道那武器的威力嗎
Are you aware of what that weapon does?

654
00:44:48,777 --> 00:44:51,127
人族帝國已經耗盡了所有資源
The Terran Empire's burned through its resources.

655
00:44:51,127 --> 00:44:52,602
饑荒肆虐 餓殍遍地
There's famine.

656
00:44:52,602 --> 00:44:55,102
整個生態系統正在崩潰
Entire ecologies are collapsing.

657
00:44:55,102 --> 00:44:57,202
它們需要尋找新的領土
They need to find a new territory

658
00:44:57,203 --> 00:44:59,327
進行征服和壓榨
to conquer and strip-mine.

659
00:44:59,327 --> 00:45:01,506
當他們意識到他們的超級武器不見了
When they realize that their superweapon is gone,

660
00:45:01,507 --> 00:45:03,552
他們一定會找到那條通道
they're gonna find that passageway--

661
00:45:03,552 --> 00:45:05,252
你知道他們會的 然後來到這裡
you know they will-- and they'll come

662
00:45:05,252 --> 00:45:08,581
燒殺搶掠每一寸領土 再奴役餘生
and they'll burn everything they touch and enslave the rest,

663
00:45:08,581 --> 00:45:12,202
您的帝國向來如此 陛下
because that's what the Empire does, Majesty.

664
00:45:13,102 --> 00:45:14,902
他們學您學到了精髓
They learned well from you.

665
00:45:17,152 --> 00:45:18,723
還有誰想要它？
Who else wants it?

666
00:45:18,724 --> 00:45:21,202
我真的不知道
I-I don't know, man.

667
00:45:21,202 --> 00:45:23,502
我收到了一個報價 錢是真的
I got an offer. The money was real.

668
00:45:23,502 --> 00:45:25,802
有人偷走了我們的天賜之物
Someone stole the Godsend from us.

669
00:45:25,802 --> 00:45:26,777
究竟是誰
Who was he?

670
00:45:26,777 --> 00:45:27,927
我真不清楚
No idea.

671
00:45:27,927 --> 00:45:31,452
無論是誰闖入我的套間 偷走了那件武器
Whoever broke into my room, whoever stole that weapon,

672
00:45:31,452 --> 00:45:32,452
知道這些事的人
they know what they know 

673
00:45:32,452 --> 00:45:34,227
肯定是從你們其中之一得來的
because they learned it from one of you.

674
00:45:53,893 --> 00:45:56,729
緊急傳送
Emergency transporter.

675
00:46:31,531 --> 00:46:32,477
這下好了
Well, this is great.

676
00:46:33,677 --> 00:46:35,427
更棒了
Oh, even better.

677
00:46:35,427 --> 00:46:37,452
那是我們的船嗎 船炸了嗎
Is that... is that the ship? Is the ship gone?

678
00:46:37,452 --> 00:46:38,752
我還挺喜歡那艘船的
I liked that ship.

679
00:46:38,752 --> 00:46:39,952
什麼情況
What happened?

680
00:46:40,627 --> 00:46:42,208
有人搞破壞
Sabotage.

681
00:46:45,577 --> 00:46:46,811
什麼
What?

682
00:46:46,812 --> 00:46:49,382
偷走天賜之物的人有一個同夥
Whoever stole the Godsend had a partner.

683
00:46:49,382 --> 00:46:51,252
就在我們幾個之中
It was someone here.

684
00:46:53,319 --> 00:46:55,902
這意味著我們中的一個是內鬼
Which means one of us is a mole.

685
00:47:02,527 --> 00:47:03,327
可能是你
Could be you.

686
00:47:03,327 --> 00:47:04,227
原話奉還
Could be you.

687
00:47:04,877 --> 00:47:08,102
要是我的話 我早把你們都殺了
If it were me, I would have murdered all of you already.

688
00:47:08,102 --> 00:47:09,827
大哥 你是了解我的
Look, boss, if there's a mole,

689
00:47:09,827 --> 00:47:10,627
絕對不可能是我
you know it's not me.

690
00:47:10,627 --> 00:47:13,002
雖然這話聽起來也就很像內奸說的 我也不確定
I mean, that sounds pretty moley to me. I don't know.

691
00:47:13,802 --> 00:47:15,377
我們合作過差不多十次了
We've been on like ten ops together.

692
00:47:15,377 --> 00:47:17,627
是沒錯 但我連你長什麼樣都不知道
Yeah, and I still don't even know what you look like, do I?

693
00:47:17,627 --> 00:47:19,212
沒人知道查莫人長什麼樣子
No one knows what a Chameloid looks like.

694
00:47:19,212 --> 00:47:21,027
你可以變成任何你想變的樣子
You might change into anything you want.

695
00:47:21,027 --> 00:47:22,182
那法茲呢
What about Fuzz, huh?

696
00:47:22,182 --> 00:47:24,127
他的體型與其他人都不在一個尺度上
He exists on a whole other scale than anybody else.

697
00:47:24,127 --> 00:47:24,852
轉移話題是嗎
Mm, deflecting?

698
00:47:24,852 --> 00:47:28,127
我的妻子即將產下我們的第一窩卵囊
My wife is about to lay our first litter of egg sacs.

699
00:47:28,127 --> 00:47:31,552
而且我還有19萬隻幼崽正在路上
No, I have 190,000 hatchlings on the way...

700
00:47:31,552 --> 00:47:32,827
- 我希望他們活下去  - 那你聽著
- and I want them to live.  - Well, look,

701
00:47:32,827 --> 00:47:34,352
你可以在我們中的任何人找到動機
you could find a motive for any of us.

702
00:47:34,352 --> 00:47:36,652
也可能是你們中任何兩個的組合
Or it could be a combination of any of you.

703
00:47:36,652 --> 00:47:38,527
你看 就像澤弗和法茲或者其他
You know, like-like Zeph and-and Fuzz or...

704
00:47:38,527 --> 00:47:40,827
你還漏掉了梅爾
You are spinning out without Melle.

705
00:47:40,827 --> 00:47:42,127
你根本沒法做出判斷
You cannot land on a choice.

