Grip,

882
00:56:10,936 --> 00:56:12,117
脊灰
Polio,

883
00:56:12,117 --> 00:56:13,477
流感
Influensina,

884
00:56:14,037 --> 00:56:14,957
牛痘
Cowpox...

885
00:56:14,957 --> 00:56:16,417
你在念什麼呢
What are you saying?

886
00:56:16,417 --> 00:56:18,477
我正在背誦我即將孵化的幼崽的名字
I'm reciting the names of me hatchlings.

887
00:56:19,496 --> 00:56:21,336
既然你們中的一個要謀殺我
Since one of you is going to murder me,

888
00:56:21,336 --> 00:56:22,696
我應該是見不到他們了
I'm never gonna meet them,

889
00:56:22,696 --> 00:56:23,976
但至少我可以這樣紀念他們
but at least I can honor them

890
00:56:24,656 --> 00:56:25,925
一個接一個
one by one.

891
00:56:26,197 --> 00:56:27,157
旅行
Trip,

892
00:56:27,697 --> 00:56:28,657
旅行二世
Trip 2,

893
00:56:29,336 --> 00:56:30,676
扁桃體炎
Tonsilyitis,

894
00:56:30,676 --> 00:56:32,016
克里米亞-剛果出血熱
Crimean-Congo Hemorrhagic Fever...

895
00:56:32,797 --> 00:56:35,197
你要哭著念完19萬孩子的名字嗎
Are you gonna sob out 190,000 names?

896
00:56:35,197 --> 00:56:37,377
你怎麼能這麼冷漠 如此無情
How can you be so cold and insensitive?

897
00:56:37,377 --> 00:56:39,016
他有可能記錄下了發生的一切嗎
Might he have recorded what happened?

898
00:56:39,016 --> 00:56:39,976
當然
Sure.

899
00:56:39,976 --> 00:56:42,557
只是這段視頻很可能和他一起被謀殺了
Except the footage was probably murdered along with him.

900
00:56:42,557 --> 00:56:45,197
我們可以將三錄儀連接到外骨骼裝甲上
We could connect one of the tricorders to his suit.

901
00:56:45,517 --> 00:56:46,776
就算沒剩多少數據
Whatever data is left,

902
00:56:46,776 --> 00:56:48,177
兇手也昭然若揭了
we'll know who did this.

903
00:56:48,177 --> 00:56:50,997
說得好像我們都是嫌疑人一樣
You say that like we're all suspects.

904
00:56:50,997 --> 00:56:52,696
並不是 好嗎
We're not. All right?

905
00:56:52,696 --> 00:56:56,097
那時候我 法茲和喬久都在那艘船裡
Fuzz, me and her were in the scow when all this happened--

906
00:56:56,097 --> 00:56:58,157
每個人都在彼此的視線範圍內
everyone in sight of everyone else.

907
00:56:58,157 --> 00:57:00,692
沒一個人亂跑 沒錯吧
And nobody went anywhere, right?

908
00:57:01,717 --> 00:57:02,808
對啊
Right.

909
00:57:05,557 --> 00:57:08,616
這不是澤弗的
Oh, this is not Zeph's.

910
00:57:09,557 --> 00:57:12,357
深褐色頭髮 25厘米
Brunette. 25 centimeters.

911
00:57:28,536 --> 00:57:29,621
這太瘋狂了
This is insane.

912
00:57:29,621 --> 00:57:30,817
別再坐立不安了
Stop fidgeting.

913
00:57:30,817 --> 00:57:32,917
我已經和澤弗近距離接觸了一週了
I've been in close quarters with Zeph for a week.

914
00:57:32,917 --> 00:57:34,696
行 所以你喜歡機甲什麼的
Okay, so you're into mecha boom-boom.

915
00:57:34,696 --> 00:57:36,495
很多人類都是 不必害羞
Lots of humans are. No shame.

916
00:57:40,577 --> 00:57:41,816
<i>檢測到血液</i>

917
00:57:43,496 --> 00:57:44,677
呃 那不可能啊
Well, that's impossible.

918
00:58:02,457 --> 00:58:04,056
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

919
00:57:58,000 --> 00:57:59,379
<i>痕跡匹配</i>

920
00:58:04,056 --> 00:58:06,926
為什麼你的指甲縫裡會有澤弗的血
why is Zeph's blood underneath your fingernails?

921
00:58:12,117 --> 00:58:13,557
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

922
00:58:13,557 --> 00:58:16,897
在澤弗的屍體上發現了你的證據
evidence from you was found on Zeph's body,

923
00:58:16,897 --> 00:58:19,837
澤弗屍體上的證據也在你身上發現了
and evidence from Zeph's body was found on you.

924
00:58:20,517 --> 00:58:22,157
不像星際艦隊的作風啊
Not very Starfleet.

925
00:58:22,157 --> 00:58:23,708
我問心無愧
Oh, I am very Starfleet.

926
00:58:24,337 --> 00:58:25,917
你清楚兇手並不是我
And you know I didn't do this.

927
00:58:26,997 --> 00:58:29,882
你只是害怕任何有道德準則的人
You are just terrified of anyone with a moral compass.

928
00:58:31,283 --> 00:58:35,120
但在那顆純潔的小心靈的深處
And deep down in that pure little heart,

929
00:58:36,056 --> 00:58:38,817
你其實是個混亂小妖精 沒錯吧
you're actually a chaos goblin, aren't you?

930
00:58:38,817 --> 00:58:40,897
- 我知道你是這樣的 小天使  - 別這麼叫我
- I know you have it in you, angel. - Don't call me that.

931
00:58:40,897 --> 00:58:42,897
星際艦隊發現了這樣的你
Starfleet sniffed you out

932
00:58:42,897 --> 00:58:45,656
把你放在了最能發揮你作用的地方
and put you in a place where you'd be most useful.

933
00:58:45,656 --> 00:58:48,597
31區正是為那些打破規則
Section 31 is just the place for officers 

934
00:58:48,597 --> 00:58:53,197
卻又從未真正越界的軍官準備的地方
who bend the rules, never quite break them until they do.

935
00:58:53,197 --> 00:58:56,741
而你 正好適合這裡
And you fit right in here.

936
00:59:02,097 --> 00:59:03,557
你想怎麼折磨我都可以
You can torture me all you want.

937
00:59:03,557 --> 00:59:05,985
但我堅持自己沒殺過人
You will never make me a murderer.

938
00:59:07,452 --> 00:59:08,497
住手
No.

939
00:59:23,336 --> 00:59:24,904
我們拿到錄像了
We've got footage!

940
00:59:28,657 --> 00:59:29,457
住手
Stop!

941
00:59:29,816 --> 00:59:31,110
快住手
Stop!

942
00:59:33,045 --> 00:59:34,616
這是我的裝甲
This is my suit.

943
00:59:34,616 --> 00:59:36,781
我即是裝甲！
I am the suit!

944
00:59:37,883 --> 00:59:40,251
裝甲就是我！
The suit is me!

945
00:59:40,252 --> 00:59:41,786
等一下
One second.

946
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:46,977
我們是你的朋友
We were your friends.

947
00:59:47,736 --> 00:59:48,997
曾是你的朋友
We were your friends.

948
00:59:49,896 --> 00:59:51,729
你殺不了我
You can't kill me.

949
00:59:51,730 --> 00:59:52,497
澤弗 別
Zeph, no.

950
00:59:52,497 --> 00:59:53,557
你不能
You can't kill...

951
00:59:59,637 --> 01:00:01,357
澤弗是自殺的?
Zeph killed himself?

952
01:00:01,997 --> 01:00:03,108
他為什麼要這麼做
Why would he do that?

953
01:00:04,677 --> 01:00:07,997
抱歉讓您失望了 陛下
Sorry to disappoint you, Your Majesty.

954
01:00:09,637 --> 01:00:11,736
這一切根本說不通
Look, none of this is making any sense.

955
01:00:11,736 --> 01:00:13,096
是啊 非常之不合理
No, none of it makes a lick of sense.

956
01:00:13,096 --> 01:00:14,536
他為什麼要這樣做呢
Why would he do this?

957
01:00:15,037 --> 01:00:16,257
給我幾分鐘時間
Give me a couple minutes to...

958
01:00:16,257 --> 01:00:17,197
我們沒時間了
We don't have minutes.

959
01:00:17,197 --> 01:00:19,158
那就幾秒鐘行了沒
Well, then give me a couple seconds, then.

960
01:00:22,037 --> 01:00:22,917
可能是你
Could be you.

961
01:00:22,917 --> 01:00:23,697
原話奉還
Could be you.

962
01:00:23,697 --> 01:00:25,197
但我連你長什麼樣都不知道
And I still don't even know what you look like.

963
01:00:25,197 --> 01:00:27,157
你可以變成任何你想變的樣子
You could change into anything you want.

964
01:00:27,157 --> 01:00:28,696
她是新來的 她才不在乎我們
She's new. She doesn't care about us.

965
01:00:28,696 --> 01:00:29,637
我可是星際艦隊的軍官
I'm Starfleet.

966
01:00:30,337 --> 01:00:32,216
當你在說我這套裝甲的時候
When you are talking about the suit,

967
01:00:32,725 --> 01:00:34,317
就是在說我
you're talking about Zeph.

968
01:00:34,317 --> 01:00:35,496
這可不是法茲
This isn't Fuzz.

969
01:00:35,496 --> 01:00:37,275
這個瓦肯外表不過是台機器
The Vulcan's just a machine, you know.

970
01:00:37,276 --> 01:00:38,809
我在裡面呢
I'm inside.

971
01:00:38,810 --> 01:00:40,477
這是身材羞辱
Scale-shamer!

972
01:00:40,477 --> 01:00:43,457
你絕對想不到我能進入多小的地方
You wouldn't believe the tiny spots I can get into.

973
01:00:43,457 --> 01:00:48,152
比如 身體改造組件的內部空間
For example, the inner workings of body modifications.

974
01:00:48,153 --> 01:00:49,976
當時他啟用了自動駕駛
There's an autopilot.

975
01:00:49,976 --> 01:00:52,257
這是唯一合理的解釋
That's the only thing that makes sense.

976
01:00:54,077 --> 01:00:58,230
你給瓦肯機器設定了自動駕駛程序
You set the Vulcan machine on autopilot.

977
01:00:59,731 --> 01:01:03,467
所以當時它的反應才那麼古怪
That's why its responses were so strange.

978
01:01:04,317 --> 01:01:05,237
你來不來
Aren't you coming?

979
01:01:05,697 --> 01:01:06,617
當然
Yes.

980
01:01:08,417 --> 01:01:11,475
你鑽進了澤弗的外骨骼裝甲
You flew into Zeph's exoskeleton.

981
01:01:12,117 --> 01:01:13,837
你鑽進去之後
And once you were inside...

982
01:01:13,837 --> 01:01:15,777
有人把西塔接口拆掉了
Somebody ripped out  the theta junction.

983
01:01:15,777 --> 01:01:17,237
加勒特 澤弗去哪了
Garrett, where's Zeph?

984
01:01:19,051 --> 01:01:21,637
然後你控制了澤弗的裝甲
Then you took control of Zeph's suit.

985
01:01:23,357 --> 01:01:25,637
當別人在找他的時候
While the others were out looking for him,

986
01:01:25,637 --> 01:01:27,858
你控制他溜回了通訊陣列
you made him sneak back into the antenna array

987
01:01:27,859 --> 01:01:29,496
然後發送了那些信息
and send those messages.

988
01:01:30,536 --> 01:01:32,296
不要這麼做
Don't do this to them!

989
01:01:32,897 --> 01:01:34,577
我們是你的朋友啊
We were your friends.

990
01:01:34,577 --> 01:01:37,368
然後你銷毀了所有證據
Then you destroyed the evidence.

991
01:01:37,677 --> 01:01:38,903
還殺掉了澤弗
And you killed Zeph.

992
01:01:41,117 --> 01:01:43,037
然後你再把這一切嫁禍給加勒特
And then you planted the evidence on Garrett here.

993
01:01:48,022 --> 01:01:49,557
舉起手來 法茲
Hands up, Fuzz.

994
01:01:49,557 --> 01:01:52,117
真是倒了血霉了
Oh, shite and ever shite.

995
01:01:59,457 --> 01:02:02,257
阿洛克 你不會真的要信她的鬼話吧
You're honestly gonna believe what she says, Alok?

996
01:02:02,257 --> 01:02:04,437
夸西 我們一起經歷了這麼多 你也信她的話嗎
Quasi, after everything we've been through?

997
01:02:06,998 --> 01:02:09,668
我能先說一句嗎
C-Can I just say one thing first?

998
01:02:14,797 --> 01:02:16,541
澤弗的外骨骼我還控制著呢
I'm still hacked into Zeph's exoskeleton.

999
01:02:30,255 --> 01:02:31,256
喂
Come on!

1000
01:02:36,097 --> 01:02:38,330
說好的「不拋棄任何人」呢
What happened to "no crew member left behind"?

1001
01:02:55,917 --> 01:02:57,357
快一點啊
Come on, come on!

1002
01:02:57,357 --> 01:02:58,383
靠近他們
Get us closer.

1003
01:04:09,496 --> 01:04:11,557
接住你了
I got you. I got you.

1004
01:04:11,557 --> 01:04:12,877
還好有我
Nice and easy.

1005
01:04:12,877 --> 01:04:13,736
該死
Damn.

1006
01:05:12,551 --> 01:05:15,197
你很關注黑市的動向 沒錯吧
You keep tabs on the black market, hmm?

1007
01:05:15,197 --> 01:05:16,997
你就是在那聽說天賜之物的消息的
And that's where you heard about the Godsend.

1008
01:05:16,997 --> 01:05:18,357
你在乎這些幹什麼
Why do you care?

1009
01:05:18,357 --> 01:05:20,124
家人你都下得去手
You killed your family.

1010
01:05:20,124 --> 01:05:21,793
再多點人算什麼呢
What's a few billion more people, huh?

1011
01:05:22,536 --> 01:05:25,016
天賜之物在哪 你的同謀是誰
Where is it? And who are you working with?

1012
01:05:25,016 --> 01:05:26,397
你登上了皇位
You took your crown

1013
01:05:26,397 --> 01:05:29,701
他們卻痛苦地死在你的腳邊
while they died in agony not ten feet away.

1014
01:05:30,797 --> 01:05:34,117
你奴役了你唯一的朋友
You condemned your only friend to slavery,

1015
01:05:34,117 --> 01:05:37,441
居然還有臉在最後一刻給他一些憐憫?
and then you had the balls to offer him kindness at the end?

1016
01:05:39,717 --> 01:05:41,513
你怎麼會知道的
How could you know that?

1017
01:05:41,997 --> 01:05:44,017
你終於發現了
Glad you're catching on.

1018
01:05:44,017 --> 01:05:46,285
他把你耍了 女皇陛下
He played you, Emperor.

1019
01:05:46,677 --> 01:05:48,320
桑還活著
San's alive.

1020
01:05:53,157 --> 01:05:55,460
不可能
It's not possible.

1021
01:05:57,717 --> 01:05:59,016
絕對不可能 到底怎麼回事
That's not possible. How?

1022
01:05:59,016 --> 01:06:01,833
他訓練出了對毒藥的抗藥性
He built up an immunity from that poison, you know.

1023
01:06:01,833 --> 01:06:05,003
每次只多服用很小的劑量
Teeny tiny doses over time.

1024
01:06:06,271 --> 01:06:10,056
看樣子是小混蛋又贏了一次
Once again, small shite for the win, mama.

1025
01:06:11,016 --> 01:06:12,897
他在哪
Where is he?!

1026
01:06:13,297 --> 01:06:15,096
期待他的精彩表演吧
He's gonna put on quite the show.

1027
01:06:15,877 --> 01:06:17,656
你製造了天賜之物
You built the Godsend.

1028
01:06:17,656 --> 01:06:19,576
你製造了一個怪物
You made this monster.

1029
01:06:19,576 --> 01:06:21,486
全是因為你
This is all you.

1030
01:07:05,496 --> 01:07:07,664
小心點可以嗎
Be careful, all right?

1031
01:07:08,317 --> 01:07:10,317
我讓你小心點
I said be careful.

1032
01:07:10,317 --> 01:07:12,296
我還得用它活動呢
I have to get around in that.

1033
01:07:15,949 --> 01:07:17,742
你都能買得起一百多具身體了 還在乎這一具
You can afford a hundred of them now.

1034
01:07:17,742 --> 01:07:18,943
太好了
Oh, great.

1035
01:07:19,637 --> 01:07:21,597
這個能用不就行了
I'd settle for one that works.

1036
01:07:23,416 --> 01:07:25,277
所以就是這個
So that's it?

1037
01:07:25,277 --> 01:07:26,797
無敵的天賜之物
The almighty Godsend.

1038
01:07:26,797 --> 01:07:28,277
等你做上皇帝了
When you're emperor,

1039
01:07:28,277 --> 01:07:31,917
能不能給它換個沒那麼奇怪的名字
maybe start by naming it something less confusing.

1040
01:07:37,200 --> 01:07:40,099
<i>離子風暴會聚倒計時</i>

1041
01:07:45,816 --> 01:07:47,405
跨越兩個宇宙的通道打開時
Once that passageway opens up,

1042
01:07:47,406 --> 01:07:50,477
他會聯繫人族 他們會從中進入
he contacts the Terrans, they come through.

1043
01:07:53,037 --> 01:07:54,578
然後他們會在此引爆
They're detonating it here.

1044
01:07:55,157 --> 01:07:57,857
他就會成為帝國的新寵
And he'd be the darling of the Empire.

1045
01:07:57,857 --> 01:08:00,616
發生這樣的災難 星聯就會陷入混亂
So he throws the Federation into chaos...

1046
01:08:00,616 --> 01:08:02,696
星際艦隊自顧不暇
Starfleet will start scrambling.

1047
01:08:02,696 --> 01:08:04,255
入侵的完美時機
Perfect time to invade.

1048
01:08:07,537 --> 01:08:08,817
你創造了它
You gave birth to this thing.

1049
01:08:10,877 --> 01:08:12,317
我們要如何阻止
How do we stop it?

1050
01:08:12,317 --> 01:08:13,377
沒辦法
We don't.

1051
01:08:13,377 --> 01:08:15,816
我們被困在這 追不上他
We're trapped here, so we can't follow him.

1052
01:08:15,816 --> 01:08:17,997
通訊天線壞了 我們也無法警告任何人
The antenna's destroyed, so we can't warn anybody.

1053
01:08:17,997 --> 01:08:19,303
胡扯
That is bullshit.

1054
01:08:20,817 --> 01:08:21,736
你肯定有更好的辦法
You can do better than that.

1055
01:08:21,736 --> 01:08:22,507
我做不到
I can't.

1056
01:08:22,877 --> 01:08:23,937
天賜之物就像我自己
The Godsend is me.

1057
01:08:23,937 --> 01:08:25,917
我唯一無法戰勝的就是自己
I'm the only one I could never defeat.

1058
01:08:29,677 --> 01:08:31,650
過去總是纏著你不放
The past always catches up with you.

1059
01:08:32,317 --> 01:08:33,096
不是嗎
Right?

1060
01:08:37,377 --> 01:08:39,157
但並不意味著它總能贏
Doesn't mean it always wins.

1061
01:08:42,117 --> 01:08:44,262
每個安全屋都有備用計劃
Every safe house, I have a backup plan.

1062
01:08:44,262 --> 01:08:45,717
把那艘垃圾船修好
We'll get that scow running.

1063
01:08:46,157 --> 01:08:49,133
老大 那傢伙飛不起來的
Boss, the scow won't fly.

1064
01:08:49,517 --> 01:08:50,977
沒有漸進線圈就不可能
Not without an asymptote coil.

1065
01:08:52,877 --> 01:08:54,573
我們有一個
We have one.

1066
01:08:54,573 --> 01:08:56,475
我們必須追上桑
We'll catch up with San.

1067
01:08:56,475 --> 01:08:58,017
我們要阻止他聯繫人族帝國
We'll make sure he can't contact the Terrans.

1068
01:08:59,157 --> 01:09:00,479
你早把線圈拆出來了
You ripped out the coil.

1069
01:09:00,479 --> 01:09:02,847
有內奸在 我可沒法什麼都說出來
Couldn't tell you while a mole was still running around.

1070
01:09:05,850 --> 01:09:07,686
你個混蛋
Asshole.

1071
01:09:20,298 --> 01:09:22,734
小夸 去幫她一下
Okay, Quas, give her a rip.

1072
01:09:28,557 --> 01:09:29,758
還是只有一下反應
Still just one pulse.

1073
01:09:35,797 --> 01:09:36,815
來活了 朋友們
And we're in business.

1074
01:09:36,815 --> 01:09:40,497
我們只有不到三十分鐘時間
Okay, team, we have less than 30 minutes.

1075
01:09:40,497 --> 01:09:42,437
小夸 設定航線前往新月星雲
Quas, set a course for the Crescent Nebula.

1076
01:09:42,437 --> 01:09:45,037
路上將會非常顛簸
All right, this is gonna be bumpy and bad.

1077
01:09:45,037 --> 01:09:47,077
我推測桑的星艦會有武器
I'm assuming San's ship will be armed.

1078
01:09:47,077 --> 01:09:48,917
廢話 人族帝國能有不武裝的星艦嗎
Yeah, every Terran ship's armed.

1079
01:09:49,357 --> 01:09:52,317
對方有質子加農炮 魚雷
He'll have proton cannons, torpedoes,

1080
01:09:52,317 --> 01:09:54,933
而我們只有一堆垃圾
and we are a garbage barge.

1081
01:09:55,697 --> 01:09:56,601
有啥好笑的
Why are you laughing?

1082
01:09:56,601 --> 01:09:58,737
因為我想不出來還有什麼更糟的情況了
Because I can't imagine things getting much worse.

1083
01:10:04,837 --> 01:10:05,676
出發
Let's go.

1084
01:10:16,037 --> 01:10:18,355
所以 這艘船會在自身周圍製造牽引力場
So, this thing flies around in the middle of a tractor field.

1085
01:10:18,356 --> 01:10:20,557
人們向太空裡面扔垃圾
People jettison their garbage into space,

1086
01:10:20,557 --> 01:10:22,637
然後這種駁船會拖著垃圾和力場
and the scow flies around and drags the trash

1087
01:10:22,637 --> 01:10:23,657
一起飛行
along with the field.

1088
01:10:24,596 --> 01:10:26,677
牽引力場裡塞滿垃圾之後
Once the tractor field is full,

1089
01:10:26,677 --> 01:10:28,497
就會一起把垃圾甩進星雲裡
it dumps the trash in the Nebula

1090
01:10:28,497 --> 01:10:30,277
讓垃圾在輻射裡自行分解
where it disintegrates in the radiation.

1091
01:10:31,277 --> 01:10:32,197
我就是想確認一下
I just want to be clear.

1092
01:10:32,197 --> 01:10:34,297
你是說我們最有可能用的上的武器
You're saying that our best potential weapon is

1093
01:10:34,297 --> 01:10:35,897
是用來拖垃圾的牽引光束嗎
a beam for collecting garbage?

1094
01:10:35,897 --> 01:10:36,697
沒錯
Yes.

1095
01:10:36,697 --> 01:10:37,297
那太棒了
Great.

1096
01:10:37,297 --> 01:10:39,844
提醒下 你在那指手畫腳幫不上一點忙
Hey, being judgy never helped anything.

1097
01:10:41,997 --> 01:10:42,897
你要去哪
Where are you going?

1098
01:10:42,897 --> 01:10:43,797
輪機室
Engineering.

1099
01:10:43,817 --> 01:10:45,277
如果那是我們唯一的武器
If that's our only weapon,

1100
01:10:45,277 --> 01:10:47,477
我要把所有的能量都導入那裡
I'll redirect all power to the tractor beams.

1101
01:10:47,877 --> 01:10:49,287
這計劃確實不錯呢
That's actually a good plan.

1102
01:10:50,997 --> 01:10:51,857
（加密傳訊3）

1103
01:10:51,857 --> 01:10:56,757
（加密傳訊3）
（跨越宇宙的通道）

1104
01:11:10,297 --> 01:11:11,157
我們就位了
We're in position.

1105
01:11:11,857 --> 01:11:13,357
通道很快就會打開
The passageway will open soon.

1106
01:11:14,237 --> 01:11:16,580
你知道我在這一切結束後想幹什麼嗎
Do you know what I want when this is all over?

1107
01:11:16,581 --> 01:11:18,877
這麼大的一塊空域
Just a big space, you know,

1108
01:11:18,877 --> 01:11:21,753
我要和我的小傢伙們到處亂飛
for me hatchlings to tunnel and fly around and...

1109
01:11:23,397 --> 01:11:24,497
那你呢
What do you want?

1110
01:11:24,497 --> 01:11:27,791
我要菲莉帕喬久永遠沉淪於她的失敗之中
I want Philippa Georgiou to marinate in her own defeat.

1111
01:11:28,577 --> 01:11:29,957
我明白你們之間是那種
I get you guys are all 

1112
01:11:29,957 --> 01:11:32,877
「永恆宿敵 性感的邪惡張力」之類的關係
"eternal nemesis, sexy evil tension" and stuff, but...

1113
01:11:33,297 --> 01:11:34,457
警報
Alert.

1114
01:11:34,457 --> 01:11:35,667
有飛船靠近
Incoming vessel.

1115
01:11:36,457 --> 01:11:38,602
檢測到碰撞航線
Collision trajectory detected.

1116
01:11:39,277 --> 01:11:40,872
她確實能把那玩意飛起來
Of course she got it off the ground.

1117
01:11:43,137 --> 01:11:45,275
我建議用魚雷解決他們
I say we should use the torpedoes.

1118
01:11:49,497 --> 01:11:50,337
對方發現我們了
They've picked us up.

1119
01:11:50,957 --> 01:11:52,257
光子魚雷來襲
Photon torpedo incoming.

1120
01:11:52,257 --> 01:11:53,437
擊中倒計時
Impact in five, four...

1121
01:11:53,437 --> 01:11:55,357
是時候進行規避機動了吧
Really want to take evasive action right now!

1122
01:11:55,357 --> 01:11:58,356
小夸 維持航線 護盾強度設置到最大
Quas, hold the course. Put everything in our shields.

1123
01:12:04,277 --> 01:12:05,937
她為什麼不改變航線呢
Why isn't she changing course?

1124
01:12:05,937 --> 01:12:07,557
我看起來像是算命師嗎
Do I look like a fortune teller?

1125
01:12:09,157 --> 01:12:11,937
我們有足夠的能量使用牽引光束鎖定他們嗎
Do we have enough juice to drag them with the tractor beam yet?

1126
01:12:12,536 --> 01:12:14,557
有 但我們沒法再承受魚雷的直接命中了
Yeah, but we can't take another direct hit.

1127
01:12:14,557 --> 01:12:17,497
魚雷即將命中 五 四 三
Incoming torpedo in five, four...

1128
01:12:17,497 --> 01:12:20,378
先維持航線 我們馬上就位了
Keep it steady. We're almost there...

1129
01:12:20,378 --> 01:12:20,997
閃避
Now.

1130
01:12:31,857 --> 01:12:34,659
警告 導航控制功能失效
Alert. Navigation control suspended.

1131
01:12:34,659 --> 01:12:37,395
他們在幹什麼 想拽死我們嗎
What are they gonna do, drag us to death?

1132
01:12:39,317 --> 01:12:42,217
她在阻止我和帝國取得聯繫
She's trying to stop me from reaching the Empire.

1133
01:12:46,738 --> 01:12:48,777
怎麼樣 大家沒事吧
How's everybody feeling about this?

1134
01:12:48,777 --> 01:12:49,637
這是唯一的辦法了
It's the only way.

1135
01:12:49,637 --> 01:12:50,909
這辦法有用
This can work.

1136
01:12:50,909 --> 01:12:53,157
輻射會削減他們的護盾
The radiation will wear down their shields.

1137
01:12:53,157 --> 01:12:55,677
是啊 但是輻射也會影響我們
Yeah, the thing is, the radiation hits us, too.

1138
01:12:58,457 --> 01:13:00,217
目標鎖定系統失效
Target lock malfunction.

1139
01:13:00,837 --> 01:13:03,557
魚雷無法鎖定目標 加農炮也離線了
I can't get torpedo lock. Cannons offline.

1140
01:13:04,597 --> 01:13:05,786
桑?
San?

1141
01:13:06,557 --> 01:13:08,025
桑
San.

1142
01:13:08,026 --> 01:13:09,794
桑!
San!

1143
01:13:18,477 --> 01:13:20,271
輻射已達致命水平
Radiation levels critical.

1144
01:13:21,397 --> 01:13:23,797
護盾失效 重複 護盾失效了
Shields are down. I repeat, shields are down!

1145
01:13:27,077 --> 01:13:28,146
他的呢
And San's?

1146
01:13:28,146 --> 01:13:30,217
還剩12% 仍在迅速下降
His are at 12% and falling fast.

1147
01:13:30,217 --> 01:13:31,477
等離子輻射來襲
Plasma incoming!

1148
01:13:31,477 --> 01:13:32,717
如果我們被捲入這樣的爆炸裡
We get caught with a burst like that,

1149
01:13:32,717 --> 01:13:34,257
我們就完了
and we're done.

1150
01:13:35,077 --> 01:13:36,420
這就是混亂 加勒特
This is chaos, Garrett.

1151
01:13:36,420 --> 01:13:38,177
你喜歡混亂沒錯吧
You know you love it, hmm?

1152
01:13:38,837 --> 01:13:41,497
直面它 接納它 享受混亂
Maybe let it in, make out with it a little.

1153
01:13:41,497 --> 01:13:43,177
這就是星際艦隊派你到此的原因
It's why Starfleet put you here.

1154
01:13:44,197 --> 01:13:45,837
混亂就像是我的炮友
Chaos is my friend with benefits.

1155
01:13:46,117 --> 01:13:47,997
就是這樣 越混亂越好
Yeah, Garrett, let's get messy.

1156
01:13:47,997 --> 01:13:48,677
怎麼樣
Hmm?

1157
01:13:49,437 --> 01:13:50,037
當然
Okay.

1158
01:13:50,037 --> 01:13:50,837
加油 小夸 你能行的
You got this, Quas.

1159
01:13:50,837 --> 01:13:51,637
沒問題
Uh-huh.

1160
01:13:51,637 --> 01:13:52,904
準備好了嗎
You ready?

1161
01:13:52,904 --> 01:13:54,338
桑的護盾只有4%了
San's shields are at four percent.

1162
01:13:56,337 --> 01:13:57,517
最後2%
Two now.

1163
01:13:58,337 --> 01:14:00,197
他的護盾已失效
His shields are down.

1164
01:14:00,197 --> 01:14:01,037
可以出發了
Good to go.

1165
01:14:39,784 --> 01:14:40,737
菲莉帕
Philippa!

1166
01:14:46,797 --> 01:14:49,277
我們這次
This contest only ends

1167
01:14:49,277 --> 01:14:52,330
不死不休
when one of us is dead!

1168
01:14:58,377 --> 01:15:01,471
引爆程序已啟動
Detonation sequence activating.

1169
01:15:03,041 --> 01:15:04,237
聽好了 我們納米人
See, the Nanokins,

1170
01:15:04,237 --> 01:15:05,517
不需要星際聯邦
we don't need the Federation.

1171
01:15:05,517 --> 01:15:06,437
向來如此
We never have.

1172
01:15:06,437 --> 01:15:10,197
早在你們這些龐然大物發現我們之前我們就在統治了
We ruled before you behemoths found us,

1173
01:15:10,197 --> 01:15:12,583
在你們死後 我們會再次統治
and we will rule again after you're gone.

1174
01:15:20,317 --> 01:15:22,726
猜猜誰會在待會的大爆炸中存活下來
Guess who survives very large explosions.

1175
01:15:24,597 --> 01:15:26,617
是我們納米人
Very small things.

1176
01:15:27,897 --> 01:15:29,257
好了 我先失陪了
Now, if you'll excuse me,

1177
01:15:29,257 --> 01:15:30,757
我得讓船脫離牽引光束
I need to cut our ship loose.

1178
01:15:30,757 --> 01:15:32,777
如果你的朋友在這個過程裡死了那真是抱歉
Sorry if your friends die in the process.

1179
01:15:32,777 --> 01:15:34,371
不 我在開玩笑
No, I'm joking.

1180
01:15:34,372 --> 01:15:35,857
我等不及要殺死他們了
I can't wait to kill them.

1181
01:15:35,857 --> 01:15:38,676
再見了 你個巨大狗屎
So long, you big lumps of shite!

1182
01:15:55,797 --> 01:15:56,737
誰在駕駛那艘飛船
Who's flying that?

1183
01:15:56,737 --> 01:16:00,597
根據傳感器 上面有一個微型生命
Uh, according to the sensors, one tiny life-form on board,

1184
01:16:00,597 --> 01:16:02,133
它在朝我們飛來
and it's heading right for us.

1185
01:16:05,697 --> 01:16:07,097
導彈鎖定
Plot missile lock.

1186
01:16:07,097 --> 01:16:09,540
我們只有垃圾 明白嗎 只有垃圾
We have trash, all right? Just trash.

1187
01:16:29,257 --> 01:16:30,517
但為一體
But one.

1188
01:16:30,737 --> 01:16:31,549
桑
San.

1189
01:16:39,137 --> 01:16:42,206
等待確認生物簽名
Awaiting biosignature confirmation.

1190
01:16:44,197 --> 01:16:45,137
我追蹤到法茲的穿梭艇了
I've got Fuzz's shuttle.

1191
01:16:45,137 --> 01:16:46,577
他要回到桑的船上
He's heading back to San's ship.

1192
01:16:46,577 --> 01:16:47,777
我們只能勉強跟上
We're barely keeping up.

1193
01:16:48,377 --> 01:16:48,879
跟住他
Stay on him.

1194
01:16:48,879 --> 01:16:50,897
提醒下 我們沒有任何武器
Uh, we don't have any weapons.

1195
01:16:50,897 --> 01:16:52,437
我們有一個滿載垃圾的貨艙
We have a payload bay full of trash.

1196
01:16:52,437 --> 01:16:53,737
不要跟丟那個穿梭艇
Do not lose that shuttle.

1197
01:16:53,737 --> 01:16:54,437
好吧
Okay.

1198
01:17:00,992 --> 01:17:02,459
我曾經什麼都不是
I was nothing!

1199
01:17:02,997 --> 01:17:05,295
那個男孩軟弱無力
That boy was soft, weak.

1200
01:17:05,296 --> 01:17:09,367
但在你腳下服侍的這些年教出了現在的我
But all those years under your heel taught me who I am now.

1201
01:17:10,537 --> 01:17:12,503
帝國艦隊將會穿過通道過來
The Empire's coming through that portal.

1202
01:17:12,503 --> 01:17:13,877
我的帝國
My Empire!

1203
01:17:13,877 --> 01:17:16,177
我們將統治這個宇宙
And we will reign over this universe

1204
01:17:16,177 --> 01:17:19,357
用公正又仁慈的手段 不像你
with righteous mercy, not like you!

1205
01:17:19,877 --> 01:17:25,216
從來不會有仁慈的獨裁者 桑
There are no benevolent dictators, San.

1206
01:17:30,617 --> 01:17:32,790
這是你教會我的
You taught me that.

1207
01:17:34,037 --> 01:17:36,094
我們還能回頭
We can come back from this.

1208
01:17:40,337 --> 01:17:41,932
我們可以重新開始
We can start over.

1209
01:17:57,957 --> 01:17:59,417
我愛混亂
Oh, I love chaos.

1210
01:17:59,417 --> 01:18:00,857
混亂是我的菜
Chaos is my jam.

1211
01:18:00,857 --> 01:18:02,377
我愛混亂
I love chaos.

1212
01:18:03,177 --> 01:18:05,677
加勒特 你在那裡邊幹啥呢
Garrett, what the hell are you doing down there?

1213
01:18:05,677 --> 01:18:07,377
夸西 我是個訓練有素的星際艦隊軍官
Quasi, I am a trained Starfleet officer

1214
01:18:07,377 --> 01:18:09,577
我也非常希望活得到能當上艦長的那一天
who fully intends on living long enough to be captain one day.

1215
01:18:09,577 --> 01:18:11,237
你得相信我 好嗎
You got to trust me, okay?

1216
01:18:11,717 --> 01:18:13,477
你好呀
Hi there.

1217
01:18:13,477 --> 01:18:15,337
真高興你找到了我
I'm so glad you found me.

1218
01:18:15,337 --> 01:18:16,300
你剛剛說啥了
What'd you just say?

1219
01:18:19,617 --> 01:18:20,697
是玩具說的
It's a toy.

1220
01:18:20,697 --> 01:18:22,737
看起來它來自一個德魯姆行星
Looks like it came from a Droom planet.

1221
01:18:22,737 --> 01:18:24,874
來一起找點樂子怎麼樣
Shall we do something fun together?

1222
01:18:28,037 --> 01:18:29,339
你還好嗎 星際艦隊女士
You okay down there, Starfleet?

1223
01:18:33,017 --> 01:18:35,657
哦 拜託 拜託 拜託 太好了
Oh, come on, come on, come on, come on. Yes.

1224
01:18:35,657 --> 01:18:38,317
我們不允許德魯姆科技進入聯邦
Oh, we do not let Droom tech into the Federation

1225
01:18:38,317 --> 01:18:40,858
因為他們用特瑞金作為電源
because they use Terrenium as a power source.

1226
01:18:41,857 --> 01:18:43,417
你是準備炸飛我們嗎
Oh, you're gonna blow us up, aren't you?

1227
01:18:43,417 --> 01:18:45,597
你最好希望這艘船的船體
You better hope that this ship's hull

1228
01:18:45,597 --> 01:18:47,298
用特莫礦加固過
is reinforced with Tomohite.

1229
01:19:13,417 --> 01:19:15,659
我是一名科學官
I am a science officer.

1230
01:19:16,297 --> 01:19:18,262
而科學就是受控的混亂
And science is just controlled chaos.

1231
01:19:18,537 --> 01:19:20,897
混亂 混亂 混亂
Whoa, chaos, chaos!

1232
01:19:33,717 --> 01:19:35,177
得了吧
Ah, come on.

1233
01:19:35,177 --> 01:19:37,181
起來 你個愚蠢的機器人
Get up, you stupid robot.

1234
01:19:59,337 --> 01:20:00,503
不 不
No. No.

1235
01:20:00,997 --> 01:20:02,465
不
No!

1236
01:20:06,897 --> 01:20:07,877
維持位置在法茲的飛船前
Stay in front of Fuzz's ship

1237
01:20:07,877 --> 01:20:09,117
這樣才能打開艙門往上倒垃圾
